The new documentation filtered by Julian Assange's portal is the ever-reduced cooperation between the United States and Pakistan in the field of nuclear proliferation and the high level of Pakistani production of nuclear weapons.
A dispatch from the Embassy in May, which describes communication with Pakistan as "frustrating", argues: "Transparency is often non-existent; offers of assistance remain unanswered or are eliminated".
