The group complained that the amounts quoted in the show were inaccurate.
Animators must provide solid rather than misleading information.
Regarding suicide, host Stéphane Dupont felt that suicide is a coward's gesture.
The majority of Committee members concluded that the message was that suicide should not be seen as a solution to life's problems.
"The majority of the Committee considers that the episodes of "Dupont au midi" have addressed a sensitive issue in a fair and appropriate manner."
